FT  10 JUN 92 / UK Company News: Regalian sells Frogmore stake
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Regalian Properties has sold its stake of 3.99m shares in Frogmore, another
property company, for Pounds 10.6m.
Regalian described the holding as a 'strategic stake' when it bought it last
October for Pounds 14m. It said it would give it an interest in
