its strategy of developing an investment portfolio.
City analysts assumed that Regalian was preparing to make a full bid and
that its plans were thwarted by its inability to sell a Pounds 80m block of
flats in Kensington.
Regalian acquired the holding from Southend Properties, which bought the
stake when it launched its unsuccessful Pounds 139m bid for Frogmore.
Regalian is due to announce its annual results today.
