<TEXT>
SUCCESSFUL PUBLIC listings of two of its investments helped Murray
Enterprise increase net asset value by 45.6 per cent over the six months to
March 31 and by 84.4 per cent over the year.
Net asset value of this investment trust stood at 129.6p per share on March
31 1992 against 89p on September 28 1991 and 70.3p on March 31 1991.
Two investments in the US, Fleet Call, a mobile communications company, and
