<DATELINE>
   BOCA RATON, FLORIDA
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
WR GRACE, the US speciality chemicals group, has agreed in principle to sell
its organic chemicals business and related assets to a new company organised
by Vestar Capital Partners, a private investment firm based in New York,
AP-DJ reports from Boca Raton, Florida.
