FT  09 JUN 92 / UK Company News: Thomas French in Pounds 1.2m acquisition
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Thomas French, the decorative accessories supplier, has bought British
Trimmings' curtain tape making business for a maximum Pounds 1.2m cash.
The company also announced interim pre-tax profits of Pounds 299,000,
against Pounds 329,000.
The acquisition achieved unaudited gross profits of Pounds 695,000 on
